    "excerpt":  "\u003cp\u003eThis post is our home for updates, announcements, and community news — a\u0026hellip;\u003c/p\u003e\n",
    "content":  "\t\t\u003cdiv data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"4778\" class=\"elementor elementor-4778\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4480f72 e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4480f72\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-355989c elementor-drop-cap-yes elementor-drop-cap-view-default sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"355989c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{\u0026quot;drop_cap\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;yes\u0026quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eThis post is our home for \u003cstrong data-start=\"341\" data-end=\"387\"\u003eupdates, announcements, and community news\u003c/strong\u003e — a simple place where parents, students, and supporters can follow what’s changing inside White Knight Academy. If you’re looking for structured \u003cstrong data-start=\"534\" data-end=\"558\"\u003eonline chess lessons\u003c/strong\u003e (especially for true beginners), we want you to see the roadmap clearly: what’s ready, what’s being tested, and what’s coming next.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b29d4f e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0b29d4f\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ba95e8c sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ba95e8c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch5 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"\u003eWhat We’re Working On Right Now\u003c/h5\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee5e799 sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ee5e799\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp data-start=\"729\" data-end=\"853\"\u003eHere are the key areas we’re actively shaping to make our \u003cstrong data-start=\"787\" data-end=\"811\"\u003echess classes online\u003c/strong\u003e feel structured, friendly, and effective:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"855\" data-end=\"1025\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"855\" data-end=\"887\"\u003e1) Beginner-first onboarding\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr data-start=\"887\" data-end=\"890\" /\u003eA clear starting path for students who don’t yet know how the pieces move — and a smooth placement for those who already play a little.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1027\" data-end=\"1190\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1027\" data-end=\"1072\"\u003e2) Membership packages (monthly \u0026amp; yearly)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr data-start=\"1072\" data-end=\"1075\" /\u003eSimple plans that match real schedules: one training per week (up to 4 per month), with guided practice in between.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1192\" data-end=\"1334\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1192\" data-end=\"1226\"\u003e3) Small-group coaching system\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr data-start=\"1226\" data-end=\"1229\" /\u003eConsistent groups (3–4 students) + optional \u003cstrong data-start=\"1273\" data-end=\"1295\"\u003echess tutor online\u003c/strong\u003e support when someone needs extra help.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1503\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1336\" data-end=\"1377\"\u003e4) Progress tracking that makes sense\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr data-start=\"1377\" data-end=\"1380\" /\u003eNot “activity points,” but practical progress: fewer blunders, better tactics habits, clearer plans, and smarter decisions.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4f4d8b2 e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4f4d8b2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{\u0026quot;background_background\u0026quot;:\u0026quot;classic\u0026quot;}\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c91295c sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c91295c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eChess is a war over the board. The object is to crush the opponent’s mind.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6fc325c e-con-full e-flex sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6fc325c\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cf2dcf3 elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget-divider--view-line sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"cf2dcf3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-divider\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\u003cspan class=\"elementor-divider-separator\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/span\u003e\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-59a795a sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"59a795a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"\u003eBobby Fischer\u003c/h6\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ecab5e3 e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ecab5e3\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-488837b sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"488837b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eSed ut mauris turpis. Etiam tortor sapien, vestibulum nec nulla et, malesuada commodo sem. Ut suscipit maximus quam, vel volutpat nibh ultricies eget. Nunc quis mollis dolor, vitae pellentesque ligula. Aliquam pretium porttitor risus, eget lobortis tortor facilisis quis. Curabitur imperdiet leo id purus euismod, faucibus maximus massa sodales. Etiam lobortis varius lobortis.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ce0f86c e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ce0f86c\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a28caca sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a28caca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://whiteknight.academy/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-02-copyright.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" /\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-734b2a5 e-flex e-con-boxed sc_layouts_column_icons_position_left e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"734b2a5\" data-element_type=\"container\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"e-con-inner\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-590af1a sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"590af1a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"\u003eAnnouncements \u0026amp; Community News\u003c/h2\u003e\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ee085b4 sc_fly_static elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ee085b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp data-start=\"1639\" data-end=\"1696\"\u003eHere’s what you can expect in this section going forward:\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3 data-start=\"1698\" data-end=\"1743\"\u003eAlpha \u0026amp; Beta Testing (Community Invite)\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1744\" data-end=\"1977\"\u003eWe’ll open limited Alpha/Beta spots as soon as the first flows are stable. If you want to help shape the platform — especially the \u003cstrong data-start=\"1875\" data-end=\"1901\"\u003ebeginner chess lessons\u003c/strong\u003e track — you can join early and tell us what works and what feels confusing.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2053\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"1979\" data-end=\"2002\"\u003eHow to participate:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr data-start=\"2002\" data-end=\"2005\" /\u003eComment \u003cstrong data-start=\"2013\" data-end=\"2024\"\u003e“ALPHA”\u003c/strong\u003e or \u003cstrong data-start=\"2028\" data-end=\"2038\"\u003e“BETA”\u003c/strong\u003e and include:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul data-start=\"2054\" data-end=\"2195\"\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2054\" data-end=\"2074\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2056\" data-end=\"2074\"\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"2056\" data-end=\"2072\"\u003eKid or adult\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2075\" data-end=\"2127\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2077\" data-end=\"2127\"\u003eYour level (brand new / beginner / intermediate)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2128\" data-end=\"2195\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2130\" data-end=\"2195\"\u003eYour goal (confidence, tactics, rating progress, tournament prep)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 data-start=\"2197\" data-end=\"2235\"\u003eNew Content \u0026amp; Coach-Led Sessions\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2236\" data-end=\"2253\"\u003eWe’ll announce:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul data-start=\"2254\" data-end=\"2441\"\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2254\" data-end=\"2289\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2256\" data-end=\"2289\"\u003ebeginner-friendly live sessions\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2290\" data-end=\"2336\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2292\" data-end=\"2336\"\u003etraining challenges (short weekly puzzles)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2337\" data-end=\"2384\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2339\" data-end=\"2384\"\u003efriendly online arenas/leagues for practice\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-start=\"2385\" data-end=\"2441\"\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2387\" data-end=\"2441\"\u003eQ\u0026amp;A posts where you can ask coaches what to train next\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3 data-start=\"2443\" data-end=\"2485\"\u003eCommunity Questions (Help Us Decide)\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2486\" data-end=\"2744\"\u003eTo keep this platform useful from day one, we’ll regularly ask for feedback.\u003cbr data-start=\"2562\" data-end=\"2565\" /\u003e\u003cstrong data-start=\"2565\" data-end=\"2586\"\u003eToday’s question:\u003c/strong\u003e What would you want most from a membership?\u003cbr data-start=\"2630\" data-end=\"2633\" /\u003eA) a clear learning path\u003cbr data-start=\"2657\" data-end=\"2660\" /\u003eB) more live coaching\u003cbr data-start=\"2681\" data-end=\"2684\" /\u003eC) puzzles + homework with feedback\u003cbr data-start=\"2719\" data-end=\"2722\" /\u003eD) flexible scheduling\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-start=\"2746\" data-end=\"2823\"\u003eReply with \u003cstrong data-start=\"2757\" data-end=\"2774\"\u003eA / B / C / D\u003c/strong\u003e — we’ll use this to prioritize the next release.\u003c/p\u003e\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t",
